(35, 'UHC STAFFING: ONE OF THE BEST RECRUITING AGENCIES IN HEALTHCARE INDUSTRY IN CALIFORNIA US.', 'uhc-staffing:-one-of-the-best-recruiting-agencies-in-healthcare-industry-in-california-us.', '5a0abb52b537f.jpg', '2017-01-04', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">Our passionate and collaborative approach has resulted in our being an entrusted agency with the best of staff ready for recruitment.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">With the healthcare industry facing a shortage crisis in terms of availability of qualified nurses and therapists, healthcare agencies are bending over for under qualified professionals but we are still standing tall with opportunities laced with high remuneration as the best platform<b>&nbsp;</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>for registered nurse jobs in US</b>&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">and</span><b><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;traveling nursing jobs in US.</span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></b><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The basis of an immense result oriented service like healthcare recruiting is the little niches and aftercare that healthcare providers undertake by personally interacting with their patients enabling their positive veto relative to their satisfaction with the staff and services provided to them.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Our stress on collaborative approach, which means the right professional at the right time for the most appropriate patient, has helped us to reduce any hint of mismanagement between staffing and scheduling.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Therapists are according to us prerequisite for complete healing process and their deftness in their physical and occupational sessions is essentially important. We are choosy when it comes to inviting therapists for interaction with us and our prima focus is how well can they deliver. Thus, any therapist who is looking out for<b>&nbsp;</b></span><b>occupational therapy jobs California in US</b><span xss=\"removed\"><b> or physical therapy jobs bay area in US</b>.</span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">To provide an equal opportunity to qualified personals who love travelling from all around the world we indulge in travel jobs in California US and guarantee our support and complete cooperation until their placements.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">UHC Staffing is one of the most sought after healthcare providers, nursing recruiters and travel jobs recruits in California US.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'healthcare industry,qualified nurses,healthcare agencies, registered nurse jobs in US,traveling nursing jobs in US, occupational therapy jobs California,physical therapy jobs ,   travel jobs in California ,travel jobs recruits in California ', 'BEST RECRUITING AGENCIES IN HEALTHCARE INDUSTRY IN CALIFORNIA USA', 'UHC Staffing is one of the best healthcare recruiting agency provides the best healthcare jobs in California, USA.', 'HEALTHCARE INDUSTRY IN CALIFORNIA, HEALTHCARE JOBS IN CALIFORNIA', 1),
(36, 'NEWEST TRENDS RESHAPING THE HEALTHCARE AGENCIES IN US BRING IN A SURGE OF SPECIALIZED RECRUITS.', 'newest-trends-reshaping-the-healthcare-agencies-in-us-bring-in-a-surge-of-specialized-recruits.', '5a0abdb8d60ec.jpg', '2016-12-28', '<p>\r\n‘The drift from volume to value aspect <strong> in the health care recruiting in US</strong> has substantially changed the perspective of health care industry’, says a recent article on Health care News. Initially  <strong> health care recruiters in US  </strong> sought to look at the patients merely as bank balance provisionary and their responsibilities were considered over after recruitment are now their active involvement by continuance of the after -care is changing scenario of the  <strong> medical staffing services in US </strong>. </p><p>\r\nDefinitely this trend is taking on the industry with a surge. </p><p>\r\n <strong> UHC Staffing  </strong> has gained momentum with this shift in trust level not because they have changed ways, but because they were always there with their humble approach standing out effervescently from the crowd as one of the best in  <strong> health care recruiting in US.</strong></p><p><strong>  </strong>\r\nI wonder why it took so long for the patients to become this dainty in their selection of health care needs. On contemplation I would say, it’s beneficial for both the patients and the staff recruited as it has become more like an online shopping spree where patients are tantalized by various packages and attractive presentation and they pick out the one most applicable to their requirements. For staff applicants it has resulted in sparking up not only the remuneration factor but instigating them to flaunt their qualifications and experience spooked by their over the edge excellent performance. </p><p>\r\nSo we  <strong> UHC Staffing health care agency in US  </strong> that have the best and experienced staff, emulated with value based back up,  <strong>travel jobs  </strong> in  <strong>California US  </strong> availability have targeted client age successfully on both patient and staff front. </p><p>\r\nThe best change is the stretch of objective or medical treatment to emotional and compassionate approach. Humility matters apart from professionalism. Patients are being allowed a more participative approach by inducing traits of self care or shall we say precautionary intuition and their interaction with health care agencies and their recruited staff is gaining momentum. \r\nIt has created wondrous outcomes with a three dimensional approach where we act as the bridge between the patients and staff recruited by us and an entrusted figure believed in by both our patients and our staff, making us stand straight on our front with an honest and diligent approach.</p>', 'healthcare recruiting in US,medical staffing services in US,UHC Staffing, travel jobs in California,healthcare agencies,medical treatment', 'NEWEST TRENDS RESHAPING THE HEALTHCARE AGENCIES IN US BRING IN A SURGE OF SPECIALIZED RECRUITS', 'UHC Staffing shares information about newest trends in healthcare industry in USA. We help to search the best jobs in healthcare industry.', 'HEALTHCARE AGENCIES IN US', 1),
(37, 'HOME HEALTH CARE: BOOMING TO BECOME THE FASTEST GROWING INDUSTRY', 'home-health-care:-booming-to-become-the-fastest-growing-industry', '5a0ac4d972f53.jpg', '2017-01-18', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">It is indeed wondrous how this life comes to a full circle amidst its ebbs and flows. Birth of a new born, then it’s growing up and then having babies of its own thereafter entering the golden years of old age and then the final destination. At every stage as persons we are backed by medical proficient services to live a smooth life.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Sometimes in later years patients fall prey to old age health hazards or struck with a health issue that demands medical attention at priority. It can be both expensive and strenuous for the patients to stay for long periods in a medical institution or clinic and that is where home health care steps in.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">United States being home to elderly people will more or less have more than 17% of the population more than 65 years in age by 2020 which is prone to increase the demand for caregivers who can professionally aid the elderly at home, where they are most comfortable giving substantial rise to traveling nurse jobs in USA, more so in California.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Zacks, an investment research firm concluded that in comparison to the $176.1 billion in 2013 home health care market would increase to $303.6 billion by 2020.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Home Health Care is the fastest growing industry in the US and the reports of US Bureau of Labor Statistics as in December 2015 stated that by 2014-2024 there will be 760,400 new jobs in the home health services, being the highest among all industries, creating potentials for healthcare recruiting in California.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Home health care includes either a caregiver who does not require any formal education or skilled medical staff such as nurses, physician assistants, therapists or other clinical professionals. The elderly patients are too rigid and set in their ways and for them staying at home and taken care of is extreme luxury. This sector that had initiated with just elderly care has encompassed patients belonging to any age group that are in need of home care. They might be children with special needs, expectant mothers or patients recuperating after critical injuries.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">The tremendous pace at which home health is rising is presenting a challenge to the healthcare staffing agencies to be well equipped with recruits that belong to home health sector as not having optimum staff could result in loss of revenues.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Realizing the potential of an optimized work force, UHC Staffing preferably seeks out medical professionals that are experienced in home health or are receiving training so that they could be recruited for either permanent job placements or temporary positions.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">With rising job opportunities, the pay scale is also expected to become more lucrative and in the coming years the need for professionally trained nurses and aids will reach at par with the demand for therapists.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">We at UHC Staffing are not only one of the best Medical Staffing Agencies in California but are also considered to be the best nurse recruiters in California and are adept at facing all ups and downs of the health care as we backed up by efficient, qualified and one of the best medical recruits in the business.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">If an applicant desires to take up nursing jobs, California they can easily access the home health care front with&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/\" xss=\"removed\">UHC Staffing.&nbsp;</a><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>', 'medical proficient services,traveling nurse jobs,healthcare recruiting in California,Home health care,physician assistants,clinical professionals, healthcare staffing agencies, Medical Staffing Agencies in California  , nursing jobs ', 'HOME HEALTH CARE: BOOMING TO BECOME THE FASTEST GROWING INDUSTRY', 'UHC Staffing provides information about home healthcare jobs in USA. Find the best home healthcare jobs in California, USA.', 'home healthcare jobs in USA', 1),
(38, 'IMMIGRATION OF THERAPISTS TO USA BY HEALTHCARE RECRUITERS IN CALIFORNIA.', 'immigration-of-therapists-to-usa-by-healthcare-recruiters-in-california.', '5a0ac83e53412.jpg', '2017-02-01', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">Therapist is a wide term that is inclusive of medical professionals that may either be Physical Therapists (PT), Occupational Therapists (OT) or SLP (Speech Language Pathologists). Is&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Healthcare recruiting in California</b></a></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>&nbsp;</b>easy? No! The Government makes it difficult, pretty taxing for the applicant to immigrate to the country.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">So, how do these foreign therapists enter USA?&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Direct applications are often waived off.&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/nursing.html\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Medical Staffing Services in California</b>&nbsp;</a></span><span xss=\"removed\">is preferred by&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/nursing.html\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Medical Staffing Agencies&nbsp;</b></a></span><span xss=\"removed\">with credibility.</span></p><p><b><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\">Physical Therapists&nbsp;</a><span xss=\"removed\">/</span><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/occupational-therapy.html\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;Occupational Therapist&nbsp;</a><span xss=\"removed\">/</span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/speech-therapy.html\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\">Speech Language Pathologist&nbsp;</a></b><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">USA being a highly remunerative market observes floundering of&nbsp;</span><b><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/rss.php\" xss=\"removed\">Physical Therapy jobs</a></span><span xss=\"removed\">,</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"><b>&nbsp;</b><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/rss.php\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Bay Area, SLP jobs, California</b>&nbsp;</a></span><span xss=\"removed\">and&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/rss.php\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Occupational Therapy jobs, California</b>&nbsp;</a></span><span xss=\"removed\">as it has been perceived over the years that somehow USA has critical shortage of professionals, as pronounced by the US Department of Labor certification, thus making US employers in health sector tap services of foreign therapists.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">The physical Therapists are in great demand in the US and it is being estimated that in the coming years the demand for them will outweigh their supply and there will be a supposed crisis in all the 50 states of US by 2030 as shown in the research report by American Academy of Physical Medicine and Rehabilitation.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">The applicant has to be in accordance with the US norms that are related to licensure, credentialing and an FCCPT Certificate before applying for the visa.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">It is essential that the candidate acquires the §343 certificate that is a prerequisite to applying in the US as therapist as it signifies that the foreign applicant’s education, experience, training, and English proficiency are equivalent to that of a U.S. medical professional.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Now, it is not as easy as it appears. US Government has strict norms regarding them but&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/home-health.html\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Healthcare Agencies in California</b></a>&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">assists the foreign therapists in becoming easily accessible to the US clients.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">There are many stringent formalities regarding immigration to the US and a direct application may be rejected but once the applicant has registered with the UHC Staffing and wants to work in The US in any niche of therapy it becomes our responsibility to evaluate all the educational certificates and other credentials necessary for the same and effortlessly get the candidate placed in the US.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The procedure for placement in the US after registering with&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>UHC Staffing</b>&nbsp;</a></span><span xss=\"removed\">is-</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">We inspect the application based on three criterions-</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Experience</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">:</span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;Having prior work experience as a therapist counts in US territory and internationally acclaimed institutions are preferable.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Education:</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;The applicant should have educational background that is approvable by the USCIS-authorized credentialing agencies. Once they give a green signal and their permission, it becomes easy for the applicant to enter US.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Fluency in English:</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">The foreign applicants have to be well versed in English as they are required to undergo the Test of English as a Foreign Language (TOEFL) exam to check their proficiency in the language before applying for the visa.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">After reviewing the application we conduct a critical interview to leave no loop holes and explain the candidate all terms and conditions of working in the US. We forward the credentials to our US employers and on approval we start procedural formalities for the therapist to work in the US making their dream of getting placement under&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://uhcstaffing.com/traveler-recruiting.html\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Travel Jobs, California</b>&nbsp;</a></span><span xss=\"removed\">easy.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">The file is sent to the Foreign Credentialing Commission on Physical Therapy for approval. It verifies the credentials and with its reports forwards it further to the licensing authorities with recommendations.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">The file after approval is taken for Visa screen certificate and on inspection of the credentials in relation with US immigration laws if approved then after documentations the application is sent for filing of visa.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Temporary Working Professional Visa:</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The H-1B visa is the visa for temporary working available for a maximum of six years during which period the therapist may also apply for permanent residency.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Permanent Residency Visa:</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Bypassing all lengthy procedures a therapist can directly apply for the I-140 Immigrant Visa for Alien worker under Schedule ‘A’ which states that since the work of US based professionals will not be affected by the immigration of therapists the so called alien workers can be permitted to enter the country. Once the applicant finds a US employer, applying for the visa for permanent residency becomes easy provided they have complied with all other regulations authentically.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Job opportunities in USA for the therapists are tremendous and highly lucrative as physical therapy is a field where US born or educated therapists are found legibly low as compared to their requirements.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Physical Therapists,Occupational Therapists ,Speech Language Pathologists,Medical Staffing Services in California,Medical Staffing Agencies,SLP jobs, Travel Jobs California ', 'IMMIGRATION OF THERAPISTS TO USA BY HEALTHCARE RECRUITERS IN CALIFORNIA.', 'Find information about IMMIGRATION OF THERAPISTS TO USA BY HEALTHCARE RECRUITERS IN CALIFORNIA.', 'IMMIGRATION OF THERAPISTS', 1),
(40, 'CAN OBAMA CARE POLICY OUTLIVE TRUMP\'S PRESIDENCY', 'can-obama-care-policy-outlive-trump\'s-presidency', '5a0acfe7b3172.jpg', '2017-03-10', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">The change of guard in the American Political Establishment in January,2017,from Obama to Trump is seen by many analysts as a harbinger of radical transformation.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">President Donald Trump has proposed drastic changes to the existing administrative and policy reforms - cutting across businesses, industries and the working class.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">One of the sectors that is likely to be impacted by Mr.Trump\'s impending policy amendments is - Healthcare System across US.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Mr.Trump’s first act as President was ,to persuade the government agencies to defer the implementation Obama Care Policy.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">What is Obama Care Policy? What would the repealing of this policy mean for the US government and its citizens? What would be the underlying repercussions of policies proposed by President Trump? How will this impact the healthcare system?&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Obama Care :</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">This is a crucial health care initiative propounded by former President Mr.Barack Obama in the year 2010.Under the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act (PPACA),populary known as ObamaCare- uncapped health insurance coverage is made available to one and all ,thereby reducing the cost of healthcare.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">This care ensures that people with pre-existing medical conditions are also able to avail of insurance ,without being rejected or over charged.Obama care has made Primary,Secondary and Tertiary Care treatment affordable and available to common man.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Studies conducted at Harvard shows that, thousands of lives are being saved every year, as patients manage to get the requisite treatment at affordable costs.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>President Trump’s Proposed Initiatives :</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;President Trump is keen on repealing the healthcare friendly and widely acclaimed Obama Care policy.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Trump administration is of the view that the Obama Care program is a death knell as majority of the insured people are the aged and sick. Republicans are keen to get rid of this scheme by cutting down the monetary source of the scheme (taxes accrued from high-income individuals). Be that as it may,the alternatives proposed by the Republicans are inadequate and unviable.</span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>No viable alternative in sight :</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>&nbsp;</b>As such ,US Healthcare System has its own inherent complexities in terms of providing insurance. The ambit of insurance covers the following vital areas : employer-sponsored coverage, Medicaid, the individual insurance market, and taxes.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">In the event of Obama Care Policy being made redundant by the Trump administration -there would be far reaching repurcussions to say the least. There are millions of Americans who are dependent on the government for medical aid. The withdrawal of Obama Care would not only affect healthcare of millions ,but also result in fiscal crisis across states- if funding of Obama Care program is withdrawn.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">The dilemma faced by Trump administration is two fold: whether to repeal Obama Care or alleviate tax deduction of high income individuals.Repealing of Obama Care, without providing an alternative means of security cover, will be an untenable proposition for President Trump. There is also a stiff opposition from Republication constituencies, in terms of phasing out of Obama Care Policy.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">In case of a stalemate,the Republican Party is likely to defer the repeal of Obama Care, and educate insurers to look for young and healthy prospects.It is also proposed that the states which did not co-operate with Obama regime, will join hands with the Republicans –with Trump owing “Insurance for everybody”.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Healthcare Providers remain Optimistic:</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>&nbsp;</b>How Trump approaches healthcare – only time will tell. People in general maybe worried, but,healthcare providers continue to exhibit a positive outlook-as the demand for medical workforce continues unabated.</span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>', 'Healthcare System ,Obama Care Policy,medical workforce,individual insurance market,Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act', 'CAN OBAMA CARE POLICY OUTLIVE TRUMP\'S PRESIDENCY', 'Find detailed information about; CAN OBAMA CARE POLICaY OUTLIVE TRUMP\'S PRESIDENCY', 'healthcare system, obama care policy, trump care policy', 1),
(41, 'GROWING TREND OF HOME HEALTH SERVICES ACROSS AMERICA', 'growing-trend-of-home-health-services-across-america', '5a0ad195ced3c.jpg', '2017-04-10', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">Global healthcare is undergoing a dramatic and revolutionary change in present times to deliver a more effective and proficient care with the shift being considered as the new normal for the healthcare sector. This continuum of care sector driven by integration and technology is enabling the people to become more connected, raising their awareness and enabling them to understand healthcare sector intrinsically.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Home health services that were just a fragment of the vast healthcare sector a few years back have emerged to be an important part of it with an upward plunge in recent times with an increased focus on value based caring in comparison to volume based care.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Home Health Services refer to :</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The basis of Home Health Services lie in the humane inherent qualities that lie dormant within one and enforces them to come a little closer to becoming a child, a partner, a companion to someone.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Patients require compassion and skilled care while recuperating from a severe illness or traumatic injury and their chances of recovering become faster if they receive those specialized services in surroundings which are comfortable for them. What more could a patient want than staying at home and also benefiting from quality and comprehensive treatment program especially designed for them laced with a skilled professional caregiver aka companion.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Insistent drive towards Home Health Services&nbsp;</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Though Home health is at crossroads in America, it has somehow managed to gain momentum and significance and is the most understood service in US today. Reasons why people are being lured towards this sector are varied and are taking the healthcare sector by force.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Ageing Citizens</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>:</b> The ageing citizens require compassionate care underlined with skilled deliverance, the prima reason why home health has picked up pace. According to the Statistics Report of U.S. Census Bureau population aged above 65 years was 40,267,984 in the year 2010. It is further expected to rise to 55,969,000 in the year 2020 to 72,774,000 in the year 2030 will further enhance the need for home health services.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Chronic Diseases</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>:</b> Patients recovering from chronic disease require skilled care that does not trigger off mental disorders. Thus steps in the home based care sector which takes care of all the needs of such patients. According to RAND people affected with chronic diseases are expected to raise almost 1% every year until 2030 that would substantiate to 37% or rather an increase of 46 million people which will further shift the home health graphs to an upward trend.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Increased threat of Post Hospital Syndrome:&nbsp;</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">As presented by Dr. Harlan Krumholz in the New England Journal of Medicine, it was evidently stressed that hospital environment creates anxiety in patients and makes them more vulnerable to developing psychological stress that in the long run is hazardous for their health. This syndrome has emerged as a potential indicator of the shift to home based services.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Preferentially stressed by Patients&nbsp;</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>:</b> Focus on quality and value based care has given a new dimension to patients where they can be treated within their comfortable zone. According to AARP, citizens falling in the age group of 54-65 with disabilities prefer to stay at home and be cared for. Even patients with 24 hour care requirement prefer to be taken care of within their homes rather than nursing homes.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Growing Trends :</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Home health care service that took shape in the USA in the 1880’s has grown ever since to become one of the most sought after industry and fastest growing segment in the Healthcare Sector presently. The number of agencies providing home health care in the United States grew from 8,314 in 2005 to 12,613 in 2013 and as per reports at present there are almost 12,057 Medicare-certified home health agencies and 23,405 other home care companies in the United States.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">It is being presumed according to surveys that medical professionals with critical expertise to deliver home services will be in much demand over the coming years increasing the value stressed care and its preference by patients, its cost effectiveness and high quality therapeutics. Though home health services accounts to only 3% of the healthcare industry, the annual growth in Home health services is estimated to be 9%.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics (BLS) stated that the growth rate in home healthcare services would further observe a growth of 5% from 2014-2024 which would account to almost 760,400 new jobs.</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">UHC Staffing, one of the leading healthcare staffing agencies in the USA foresees tremendous growth in the home healthcare services and believes that with just a few modifications in the implementation of existing strategies and understanding the relevance of home health services in accordance with value rather than volume, revision of existing system that has certain loop holes regarding medical benefits and payments, home health services is likely to become the most unparalleled sector of health care in the coming times.</span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>', 'Global healthcare ,healthcare sector ,Home Health Services ,traumatic injury ,skilled professional caregiver ,Chronic Diseases  , mental disorders   ,Post Hospital Syndrome  ,psychological stress , Bureau of Labor Statistics  ,healthcare staffing agencies', 'GROWING TREND OF HOME HEALTH SERVICES ACROSS AMERICA', 'UHC Staffing share GROWING TREND OF HOME HEALTH SERVICES ACROSS AMERICA.', 'HOME HEALTH SERVICES, HOME HEALTH USA', 1),
(42, 'HEALTH CARE MARKET IN CALIFORNIA: WIDE RANGING AND LUCRATIVE', 'health-care-market-in-california:-wide-ranging-and-lucrative', '5a0ad312a0a71.jpg', '2017-08-01', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">Spread over an area of 423,790 square kilometers, California, a western US state with a population density of over 39.25 million (as per 2016 census), perhaps the most diverse in the nation is often referred to by its nickname, The Golden State.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Healthcare Market in California is vitally interlinked to its economy and in spite of the tremendous challenges faced by it; the industry is expected to increase further over the next few years perhaps at a much higher pace than the present, owing to several factors.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Area – Wise Market Potential</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">California being a large state encompasses many regions within it. As an insight into the main regions that provide job opportunities to health care workers, analysis bring out that&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Healthcare workers that were estimated to be around 299, 230 in 2010 in the Los Angeles-Long Beach-Glendale Metropolitan Division are expected to rise by nearly 120,000 or 40% by the year 2020.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The Santa Ana-Anaheim-Irvine Metropolitan Division is expected to provide jobs to more than 102,450 healthcare workers by 2020.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Job Outlook and Wages</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Presently California is engaged in 31 healthcare occupations with abound opportunities for job seekers in the industry. Growth in some major areas.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In the period of 2014-2024, employment opportunities for Physical Therapists are expected to rise from 19,300 to 24,500. Hourly wages they are being handed out is $46.42 (2017).</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Hourly wage of Licensed Vocational Nurses (LVN) is $ 25.64 (2017) with employment opportunities projected to rise to 79,400 from 65,700.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Home Health Aides, another important occupation are being paid an hourly wage of $14.43 and the expected rise in their employment opportunities is 45,700 from 32,900.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Factors affecting Healthcare Market&nbsp;</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Registered Nurses, perhaps the largest group in the Health care industry are being paid $ 75,840 to $ 141,030 annually.&nbsp;</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\">Demand for specialized health care aides in California is gradually gaining momentum being spurred on by the need to take care of the increasing aging population of the Californian State.</li><li xss=\"removed\">Health Care job opportunities in California have increased enormously instigated by stringent implementation of the Medical Care Plans inducing people to seek coverage under health care insurance.</li><li xss=\"removed\">Registered Nurses have gradually replaced the aging health care providers on the brink of their retirement and are expected to further take command of the market with a surge.</li><li xss=\"removed\">The critical current shortage of primary health care providers owing to lack of educational infrastructure facilities and efforts put in by the sectors is being worked upon steadfastly by the authorities of the Californian State, educators and private and public sectors jointly.</li><li xss=\"removed\">Technological advances have improved the dispensation of Healthcare Services in California bringing significant changes in the patient care strengthening the communication between patients and healthcare providers.</li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Thus, California is a wide and lucrative market for the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.uhcstaffing.com/\" target=\"_blank\" xss=\"removed\">Healthcare Agencies&nbsp;</a><span xss=\"removed\">and providers developing at a fastidious pace. Anticipated increase in job and salary is making California a major employment hub and the highest paying state in US.</span></p>', 'Healthcare Market ,Healthcare workers,Physical Therapists ,Licensed Vocational Nurses ,Home Health Aides ,Registered Nurses, Health Care job ,   Medical Care Plans  , health care insurance , Healthcare Services in California  ', 'HEALTH CARE MARKET IN CALIFORNIA: WIDE RANGING AND LUCRATIVE', 'UHC Staffing provides information about healthacre market growth in Caliornia, USA.', 'HEALTH CARE MARKET IN CALIFORNIA', 1),
(43, 'SOCIAL MEDIA RECRUITING; PROACTIVE APPROACH TO HELP EMERGENCE OF NEW GENERATION OF HEALTH CARE PROFESSIONALS', 'social-media-recruiting;-proactive-approach-to-help-emergence-of-new-generation-of-health-care-professionals', '5a0ad7e62c416.png', '2017-08-30', '<p><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Social Media Recruiting; Proactive Approach to help emergence of New Generation of Healthcare Professionals</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">“Hold the vision, trust the process”</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Social Media has opened a new arena, an unparalleled world in Healthcare Recruiting. With Technology as a tool by their side the companies and staffing agencies are recruiting a completely new generation of best healthcare professionals and enabling healthcare industry to embrace these changes with open arms.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">It was in the late 1900’s and 2000’s that on line platform for job search and recruitment gained momentum. It became easy to outreach Global employers and medical candidates. As array of opportunities opened wide, so did the trend in social recruiting even though Healthcare was perhaps the slower sector to pick up the concept.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">As per survey it was observed that year 2012 became the year to mark the significant presence of Social Media Recruiting pervasive. Over the years now it has become the language of communion, a way of functioning that has helped passive and dormant talent to emerge and reach out to their dreams.&nbsp;</span></p><p><a href=\"http://www.uhcstaffing.com/\" target=\"blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>Healthcare Staffing Agencies</b></a><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;are executing social media recruitment in the form of a well processed and worked out game plan. They observe the trends, enter the loop holes and strike their targets. The more observant and skilful executioner the agency emerges to be, the better the chances of sustaining and improving their business becomes carried out by facilitating job placements to the candidates and efficient medical staff to the employers.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Social Media Marketing has become synonymous to Facebook, LinkedIn and other social media sites that were unheard of a few years back which leaves us to wonder when out of the spree we might get to witness another new era of articulate and finessed social media recruitment taking the world of healthcare to maybe a further upward plunge.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Just be on your feet and run as fast as you can to catch up with the changes else you will be left far behind.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Now where&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><a href=\"http://www.uhcstaffing.com/\" target=\"blank\" xss=\"removed\"><b>United Healthcare Staffing&nbsp;</b></a></span><span xss=\"removed\">does steps in, you may wonder? Or how adept is it in recruiting allied healthcare professionals?&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Well, UHC are strategic planners and with a network that reaches out worldwide have reliable, consistent and deft professionals. Once the recruits register themselves with the agency the responsibility of their placements is carried out in a swanky and trendy yet stringent focused approach. We see to it that all our employees reach their desired destinations and soar high in life. From the point of registration, to building up their impressive social profiles and displaying their inherent talents, to finally having them well settled in their jobs, we are there with them, each step of the way.&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>', 'Social Media Recruiting , Healthcare Professionals,healthcare industry,medical candidates,Social Media Marketing', 'SOCIAL MEDIA RECRUITING; PROACTIVE APPROACH TO HELP EMERGENCE OF NEW GENERATION OF HEALTH CARE PROFE', 'UHC staffing helps new generation to get jobs in social media health care. Visit our website for more details about social media health care.', 'SOCIAL MEDIA RECRUITING', 1),
(44, 'HOME VISIT OF WELL TRAINED AND EXPERIENCED REGISTERED NURSES AND THERAPISTS: A NEW BEGINNING', 'home-visit-of-well-trained-and-experienced-registered-nurses-and-therapists:-a-new-beginning', '5a0ada9f54a46.png', '2017-09-02', '<p><span xss=\"removed\">As a Healthcare Staffing Agency we are often sought assistance from family members of patients who are in a dilemma to seek the best and most appropriate choice for their loved one.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Placing their loved ones under the wings of specialized medical care is often an unnerving decision for the family. Uncertainty and anxiety harbingers on their minds while selecting between the options available.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">Patients who need skilled care after a trauma that has left them both emotionally and physically impaired or elderly patients who are suffering from some grave conditions, like cancer, diabetes, multiple sclerosis or Alzheimer’s disease are often stuck between the choice to be in-patients at a hospital/ nursing home or be taken care of within the comforts of their home where in home care emerges out as the winner in maximum cases.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">This is just the beginning! Now comes the part where the family members have to firmly shortlist on what or who they want to take care of their loved one. The choice varies between an in-home personal aide and in-home registered nurse.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Whereas Personal Care Aides take care of patients and stay with them as their personal companions, doing all chores for them, they do not necessarily hold expertise to cope with critical medical contingencies. With limited capabilities they act as an emotional umbrella to the patients and are usually handed out somewhere around $9 to $30 per hour.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Registered Nurses are invariably sought for patients who need skilled nursing services. Indispensable in their dispensation by monitoring vital parameters, medications, caring of the wounds, therapy, RN Nurses charge somewhere from $25 to $50 per hour. Their cost varies depending on several factors such as their number of visits, the length of their visit, and their service.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Services of the therapists are pursued when patients have lost mobility or sensation in a body part due to a traumatic injury and cannot cope with their impairment. Physical Therapists or Occupational Therapists gradually help restore motion back in the patient’s body by exercising regime and teach them how to cope with their surroundings in spite of their disability.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The therapists /Registered Nurses may enter into an agreement with the patients where they extend their services on per visit basis. This provides them an opportunity to work according to their preferences and terms. The underlined concept here is ‘more the visits more the remuneration.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">We can easily refer to it as a part time job which is beneficial for both the patients and the skilled aides. Patients are reviewed intently, they receive personal care on each visit and their minute problems are attended to, at every visit.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Depending upon the travelling expenses spent on visits, number of hours that are put in to review the patients, proficiency required for the dispensation of the service, time of the day when the patients are visited and whether it is a routine or an emergency visit are often the deciding factors of the cost that is charged by them.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">At United Healthcare Staffing, an experienced and creditworthy agency we are striven towards unabridged customer contentment and maximum remunerative jobs for our medical recruits. We provide our clients with well trained and efficient nurses and therapists to provide them constant care and assist our coparceners in availing such opportunities and framework to extract the maximum according to their credentials.&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>', 'Healthcare Staffing Agency,specialized medical care,Alzheimer’s disease,home registered nurse,Registered Nurses,RN Nurses,    Physical Therapists , United Healthcare Staffing ,    medical recruits ', 'HOME VISIT OF WELL TRAINED AND EXPERIENCED REGISTERED NURSES AND THERAPISTS: A NEW BEGINNING', 'NOW HOME VISIT OF WELL TRAINED AND EXPERIENCED REGISTERED NURSES AND THERAPISTS HAVE BECOME VERY COMMON IN TODAY LIFE. FIND MORE DETAILS AT THIS PAGE.', 'REGISTERED NURSES AND THERAPISTS', 1),
(45, 'LATEST MEDICARE CHANGES', 'latest-medicare-changes', '5a0adc936d35e.png', '2017-09-13', '<span xss=\"removed\">Medicare is the National Health Insurance Program for the tens of millions of US citizens aged 65 or above, patients suffering with end stage kidney problems or any other critical disabilities. At present there are as many as 57 million beneficiaries under the plan.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">It is a kind of customary tradition with Medicare to reshape the benefits it offers, every year. Revisions observed in the Medicare Plan witness modifications in Medicare costs and coverage options and are usually announced for the next year in the months of October-November of the present year.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Speculative Outpour</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">:&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">As per Congressional Budget Office, the span period from 2016-2025 may observe an additional spending of $802 billion by Medicare, should the Affordable Care Act be repealed completely.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In continuance the Kaiser Family Foundation asserts that this additional spending is likely to be borne by the beneficiaries in the form of increased Premiums, Deductibles and cost sharing.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Another speculation that runs underneath is as Vox’s Mathew Yglesias says, “Democrats want the subsidization of health care costs of the working class be indirectly borne by the rich class, as it is a costly affair but Republicans are not in the favor. It is a wait and watch scenario as to which side the coin will flip to.”</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Changes envisaged in 2017</b></span><span xss=\"removed\">:</span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;Let us delve into each segment of the plan step by step to comprehend what they signify and changes introduced in each for the year 2017.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Premiums:</b>&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">The monthly amount paid by a Medicare enrollee seeking coverage or insurance under Medicare, is referred to as the Premium. The two types of Premiums being implemented under Medicare are-</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Premium Type A</b>&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">covering the hospitalization charges exempting premium for most enrollees who have with or without their spouse a history of 40 quarters of work history. Recent changes implemented in the aforesaid are-</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">For enrollees who have a history of more than 30 quarters of work history but less than 40 will be required to pay $227 a month in comparison to $226 in 2016.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">For enrollees who account for even lesser quarters of work history than 30 will be expected to pay $413 a month as compared to $411 in 2016.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Coming to Premium Type B covering the medical insurance and depending on the income class of the enrollee will increase more than $4 monthly amounting to $109 in the year 2017 as compared to $ 104.90 as in 2016, for 70% of them. For the remaining 30% the premium expected to be paid after a hike of 10% should fall somewhere around $134/monthly in 2017 as compared to $121.80 in 2016. The premium of the high income class is also being expected to rise to $187.50 - $428.60 monthly in 2017 in comparison to $171 -$390 per month in 2016.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Deductibles:&nbsp;</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The amount paid by a Medicare enrollee out of his pockets before it is shared by the Medicare plan is referred to as Deductibles. Deductibles are categorically distributed under part A and part B following in lieu with the premiums.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Part A Deductible in the year 2017 will be raised to $1316 in comparison to $1288 in the year 2016 covering the 60 inpatient days. Beyond the 60 days to 90 days the deductible charged per day has been fixed $329 in 2017 that is slightly higher than $ 322 in 2016.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Part B Deductible has been raised uniformly to $183 in 2017 from $147 in 2015 and $ 166 in 2016.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Part D deductible that covers Prescription Drug Plan has been ascertained to $400 in 2017.</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Therapy Cap</b></span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Benefit limit that is extended to the enrollee on an outpatient basis for physical, occupational or speech language therapy is covered by the therapy caps which are apportioned between the Medicare and the patient in the ratio of 80% is to 20%. The therapy caps have been increased further by $20 in 2017.&nbsp;</span><br xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Medicare proposes to bring further flexibility and transparency in their payment systems in the year 2018 and 2019 to facilitate the needs of the patients and result in better leveraging of the system to maximize outputs.</span>', 'National Health Insurance Program,kidney problems,Medicare Plan ,Speculative Outpour,Medical insurance, Speech language therapy', 'LATEST MEDICARE CHANGES', 'UHC Staffing shares latest medicare changes in USA and Canada.', 'LATEST MEDICARE CHANGES', 1);
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`b_id`, `title`, `slug`, `img`, `date`, `description`, `tags`, `meta_title`, `meta_description`, `keywords`, `status`) VALUES
(46, 'DIALYSIS NURSING IN HIGH DEMAND: CAREER OPTIONS AND JOB REQUIREMENTS', 'dialysis-nursing-in-high-demand:-career-options-and-job-requirements', '5a0ae02327bb2.png', '2017-09-20', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Dialysis\r\nnursing in high demand: Career options and Job Requirements</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Dialysis\r\nnursing</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"> deals with patients having chronic kidney problems. A\r\ndialysis nurse administers the process of dialysis on patients and thus offers\r\nhigh-quality of life. Since Chronic Kidney Disease has developed nowadays at an\r\nalarming rate, demand for dialysis nursing is on the rise. According to the\r\n‘American Journal of Kidney diseases\', about half of Americans above 30 years\r\nare suffering from <b>Chronic Kidney\r\nDisease ( CKD).</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Requirements\r\nfor Dialysis Nurse</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>:</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Dialysis nurses must be <b>Registered nurses (RNs) </b>or advanced practice\r\nnurses. A dialysis nurse must have minimum education, which is bachelor\'s\r\ndegree. If you can earn Master of Science in Nursing (MSN), you will be able to\r\ngrab more opportunities for advancement. You may have to take classes in\r\nnephrology, nutrition, and pharmacology. Before practicing dialysis nursing,\r\nyou need to cover the state approved the program and pass the NCLEX\r\nexamination. In other words, you need to be certified.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Duties\r\nof a dialysis nurse:</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A dialysis nurse first,\r\nimplements diagnostic tests. She makes the patients and their families familiar\r\nwith treatment options. She makes diet chart and monitors exercise program.\r\nSometimes, they make home visits. A dialysis nurse orders medical equipment and\r\ncoordinates medical treatments.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Place\r\nof work of dialysis nurses:</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b><o></o></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Dialysis nurses work in\r\nhospitals, hospice, nursing homes, home health care agencies, clinics and even\r\nin the home of the patients.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Wherever you work, your\r\nworking hours will be regular. A patient with chronic kidney disease usually is\r\nin need of dialysis procedure during the daytime. So, working hours of nurses\r\nare fixed. But in hospitals, a patient needs to take dialysis procedure at any\r\ntime. Therefore, a dialysis nurse\'s working hour in the hospital is flexible.\r\nBut don\'t worry, that type of schedule offers you a higher pay along with\r\nvaluable experience.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Reasons\r\nfor the high demand for dialysis nurses</b></span><span xss=\"removed\"><b>:</b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"># 1. The leading causes of\r\nChronic Kidney Disease are type 2diabetes and hypertension. As the US\r\npopulation is growing older, they are being affected by these diseases more and\r\nmore. So, there is always demand for dialysis nurses.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"># 2. Today, kidney\r\ntransplant procedure is successful but it is expensive. According to the United\r\nNetwork for Organ Sharing (UNOS), the charge for kidney transplant exceeds\r\n$262,000. So, naturally, dialysis nurses are still in demand.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span xss=\"removed\"># 3. According to\r\nCDC, about 10% of the American population is affected by Chronic Kidney\r\nDisease. This is one of the most important reasons for dialysis nurses.</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Dialysis travel\r\nnurses:</b></span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">There is a huge demand for <b>dialysis\r\ntravel nurses</b> all over the country because they travel for taking care of\r\npatients affected by kidney disease. <b>United\r\nHealthcare (UHC) Staffing </b>is offering higher pay and benefits to those\r\ndialysis travel nurses. Qualified registered nurses can choose locations of\r\ntheir work. Though they follow a tight schedule, they have enough freedom to\r\nchoose locations. They usually work for 13- week assignment. The dialysis\r\ntravel nursing jobs are more than the candidates applying for these jobs.</span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Salary:<o></o></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Salary of a registered\r\ndialysis nurse is $2,170 per week, which is more than that of a registered\r\nnurse, whose salary is $1,601 per week.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Registered Dialysis nurse:\r\n$2,170<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Registered nurse: $1,601<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Registered Travel Nurse: $1,380</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b>Conclusion:<o></o></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">United Health Care Staffing\r\nor&nbsp; (UHC) Staffing, </span><a href=\"http://www.uhcstaffing.com/\"><span xss=\"removed\">www.uhcstaffing.com</span></a><span xss=\"removed\"> an\r\noutstanding healthcare recruiting agency, recruits registered dialysis nurses\r\nand provides them high remuneration making the nurses substantial earner. If\r\nyou are looking for dialysis travel nurses jobs, contact with United Healthcare\r\nStaffing or UHC Staffing, who will take you under their wing and will help you\r\nto secure one of the best-paid jobs.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b><o></o></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></b></p>', 'DIALYSIS NURSING Jobs', 'DIALYSIS NURSING IN HIGH DEMAND: CAREER OPTIONS AND JOB REQUIREMENTS', 'UHC Staffing provides the best opportunity in DIALYSIS NURSING. Visit our website for getting DIALYSIS NURSING jobs in USA and Canada. ', 'DIALYSIS NURSING Jobs', 1),
(47, 'WHAT IS TRAVEL NURSING? ITS CLINICAL REQUIREMENTS', 'what-is-travel-nursing?-its-clinical-requirements', '5a0ae3c683af2.jpg', '2017-09-29', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">What\r\nis Travel Nursing? Its Clinical Requirements<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A <b>travel Nurse</b> is a nurse, who works in a location for a limited\r\nperiod of time, which ranges from 13 weeks to 26 weeks. After that she moves to\r\nanother destination and works there. Actually, they move to that part of the\r\ncountry, where they are needed. A travel nurse fulfills a gap in hospitals,\r\nmade due to extended absence of hospital staff, staff training etc. Therefore, <b>travel nursing</b> is now an important part\r\nof healthcare industry and its demand is on rise.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Bear in mind:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel nurses have the\r\nenough freedom to choose their working place and working hour. So, they can\r\ntake a leave when they want and change their job too.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Advantages\r\nof Travel Nursing:</span></b></p><ul><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\nnurses can get the benefit of free high-quality housing, which is furnished.<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">They\r\nhave freedom to choose where they will work and when they will work.<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">They\r\ntravel the entire country because they have positions in all 50 states of US.<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\nnurses get the benefits of vision, dental and medical insurance along with\r\nbonuses and incentives.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">24x7\r\nteam support and transport facility are available for travel nurses.</span></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Requirements</span></b><span xss=\"removed\">:<o></o></span></p><p xss=\"removed\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Academic Qualification:</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A travel nurse must be a Registered\r\nnurse (RN). <b>RN Nurse Recruiters</b>\r\nrecruit those nurses having 4-years degree from a hospital-based nursing school\r\nor 2 years associate degree in nursing or having 4 years BSN degree. A\r\nregistered nurse can specialize in an area of interest in nursing. Bachelor’s\r\ndegree is the minimum qualification for being a nurse.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Training:<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel nursing agencies\r\nprefer to have a nurse having a hands-on experience in her chosen area of\r\nnursing. Travel nursing agencies require a graduate, registered and trained\r\nnurse.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Certification:<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A travel nurse can obtain licensure\r\nafter passing the NCLEX-RN certification exam and can also obtain Nurse\r\nLicensure compact with the help of travel nursing agencies. This Nurse\r\nLicensure Compact helps registered nurses to become travel nurses in other states\r\nalso.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Skills and qualities:</span></p><ul><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Excellent\r\ncommunication skills <o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Ability\r\nto understand both medical and social&nbsp;\r\nneeds of the patients<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Flexibility<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Adaptability\r\nto new and changing environment<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Power\r\nto cope with new technology<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Detail\r\noriented<o></o></span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Skilled\r\nin analysis</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Power\r\nto understand local language</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\nnursing jobs</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> offer opportunities for further education\r\nand training. Further education allows nurses to become nurse practitioners or\r\nnurse educators.<o></o></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">As travel nurses are hired\r\nfor critical needs in hospitals, they earn a high salary. Besides, other\r\npackage covers housing, medical, dental insurance, bonuses, retirement saving\r\nplans etc.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o><br></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Reasons\r\nwhy nurses should consider travel nursing:</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\"><o><br></o></span></b></p><ul><li><span xss=\"removed\">There\r\nis a scope to learn about nursing when a nurse works with an experienced,\r\nfellow nurse. She learns how to take challenges and make triumphs.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">There\r\nis a chance to plan your assignment in areas, which you like to visit.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">Here\r\nis an opportunity for open communication because a nurse can upfront her needs\r\nand wants to recruiters.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></span><span xss=\"removed\">A\r\ntravel nurse can earn a good salary and benefits.</span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\nnursing helps nurses to choose specialties and localities, which they like.</span></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Conclusion:<o></o></span></b></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">\r\n\r\n</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The demand for travel\r\nnursing jobs is increasing day by day in the US. <b>United Healthcare Staffing (UHC Staffing – </b></span><a href=\"http://www.uhcstaffing.com/\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">www.uhcstaffing.com</span></b></a><b><span xss=\"removed\">)</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> is offering high salary and\r\nbenefits to registered travel nurses. Not only that, weekly payment, excellent\r\ncommunication, and good transport system are important features of UHC Staffing.\r\nIt provides an opportunity to meet with different people, to build a resume for\r\nnurses, to work in different settings. Thus, if you want to get travel nursing\r\njobs, contact with UHC Staffing.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p>', 'Travel Nursing Jobs,Travel Jobs', 'WHAT IS TRAVEL NURSING? ITS CLINICAL REQUIREMENTS		', 'UHC staffing shares details about; WHAT IS TRAVEL NURSING? ITS CLINICAL REQUIREMENTS.		', 'TRAVEL NURSING', 1),
(48, 'TRAVEL PHYSICAL THERAPY AND TRAVEL OCCUPATIONAL THERAPY: THEIR REQUIREMENTS', 'travel-physical-therapy-and-travel-occupational-therapy:-their-requirements', '5a12c44f912de.png', '2017-10-06', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\nPhysical Therapy and Travel Occupational Therapy: Their requirements<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\nphysical therapists</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> visit different locations in order to gain\r\nexperience in different clinical settings. Thus they get the opportunity to\r\nmeet new and interesting public along the way. Travel physical therapists,\r\nnowadays, are in high demand because they fill a gap in hospitals made due to\r\nabsence, training etc. This profession is adventurous since they face\r\nchallenges here.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\noccupational therapists</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> travel the entire country while working\r\nin the best clinics. Travel occupational therapy jobs can place therapists in\r\nnew and exciting locations where therapists can grow their skills along with\r\npersonal experiences.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Travel\r\nphysical therapists Vs Travel occupational therapists:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Skills:</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> Travel\r\nphysical therapists help patients to recover from injuries. They aim at getting\r\npatients back in motion with massage, exercises, and other techniques. Physical\r\ntherapists allow the patients to avoid long-term medications and surgery. On\r\nthe other hand, travel occupational therapists focuses on helping the patients\r\nto perform daily tasks, suffering from cognitive disabilities, memory loss,\r\ninjuries etc.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Requirements:</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> Graduate\r\ndegree, master\'s degree of 2 years and 3 years doctorate degree are necessary\r\nto become a travel physical therapist. In addition, to be a travel physical\r\ntherapist, experience as a physical therapist is also necessary. On the other\r\nhand, occupational therapists must be a master degree holder. A doctoral degree\r\nis optional.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Certification:</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> Physical\r\ntherapists must be licensed in the state they want to work. Similarly Occupational\r\ntherapists requires license as well. If they are working for government\r\nhospitals and VA systems they can use any state license to work in VA\r\nHospitals, separate state licensing is not required. <o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Point to be noted:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Sometimes, patients need\r\ntravel physical therapists first for recovering from injuries and then move to\r\nthe travel occupational therapists for learning daily tasks. For example, if a\r\npatient is suffering from severe injury, travel physical therapists help them\r\nto recover from it by exercise, massage etc. After getting relief to some\r\nextent, the patients take the help of travel occupational therapists for\r\nlearning combing hair, brushing tooth, walking etc.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Now:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">We shall discuss the\r\nadvantages of travel physical therapists and travel occupational therapists.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Advantages\r\nof travel Physical therapists (PTs) and travel occupational therapists (OTs):<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;If a physical therapist wants to be a travel\r\nphysical therapist, no doubt, great pay, multiple benefits, bonuses are waiting\r\nfor them. Yes. There are other reasons also why a physical therapist opts for a\r\ntravel physical therapist job. The same is for occupational therapist jobs.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"># 1<b>. Lucrative job:</b> <o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel<b> physical therapy jobs</b> or travel occupational therapy jobs offer\r\n20% more payment than permanent jobs and bonuses, allowances for completing a\r\n13-week assignment.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">#\r\n2. Opportunity to explore the country:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel physical therapy jobs\r\nor <b>occupational therapy jobs</b> offer\r\nan opportunity to choose the locations of work they want. If any travel\r\nphysical or occupational therapist wants to work in Florida in winter, she or\r\nhe can choose Florida for her work. Thus this job offers not only high pay but\r\nalso chances to explore the country of their choice.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">#\r\n3. Open the door to many settings:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel physical or\r\noccupational therapists can work in a variety of settings like leading\r\nhospitals, schools, and outpatient- clinics etc. They can choose new work\r\nsettings for different assignments.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">#\r\n4. Build the Profile:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Travel physical therapy jobs\r\nor travel occupational therapy jobs allow them to build their profile by\r\nworking in a variety of settings throughout the country with leading\r\nfacilities. Thus, they can learn new practices and gain experiences.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Conclusion:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">United\r\nhealthcare staffing (UHC Staffing)</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> provides high salary and\r\nmany facilities to travel physical and occupational therapists. Not only that,\r\nwe offer the opportunity to explore the country, to build your resume and to\r\nwork in different locations of your choice. UHC Staffing (</span><a href=\"http://www.uhcstaffing.com/\"><span xss=\"removed\">www.uhcstaffing.com</span></a><span xss=\"removed\">) is\r\nready to offer you travel physical therapist jobs and travel occupational\r\ntherapist jobs.<o></o></span></p>', 'Travel Physical Therapy ,Travel Occupational Therapy,Physical Therapy,Travel Nursing Jobs', 'TRAVEL PHYSICAL THERAPY AND TRAVEL OCCUPATIONAL THERAPY: THEIR REQUIREMENTS', 'UHC Staffing provides information about Advantages of travel Physical therapists (PTs) and travel occupational therapists.', 'travel Physical therapists, TRAVEL OCCUPATIONAL THERAPY', 1),
(49, 'VENDOR MANAGEMENT SYSTEM: ROLE OF UHC STAFFING IN STAFFING HEALTHCARE STAFF', 'vendor-management-system:-role-of-uhc-staffing-in-staffing-healthcare-staff', '5a12c9df1b8fa.png', '2017-10-16', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Vendor\r\nmanagement system: Role of UHC Staffing in staffing healthcare staff<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A web-based application,\r\nwhich is used to manage and secure staffing services on a temporary basis or on\r\na permanent basis, is known as a <b>Vendor\r\nManagement system (VMS).</b> In other words, Vendor Management System is a\r\nsolution of dealing a large amount of external hiring by an organization. VMS\r\nhelps to solve the complex problems regarding staffing. It is a web-based\r\napplication used by United Healthcare Staffing (UHC Staffing).<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The important\r\ncharacteristics of Vendor Management System include automatic billing,\r\nmanagement reporting, staff ordering, business intelligence function, amenity\r\ntracking, workflow engines and providing service catalog.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In this article, we will\r\ndiscuss advantages of Vendor Management System and role of United Healthcare\r\nStaffing in staffing healthcare staff.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Advantages of Vendor\r\nManagement System:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">1.</span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span xss=\"removed\">Monitoring\r\nthe hiring process</span></b><span xss=\"removed\">:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In case of the traditional\r\nhiring process, the hiring desk was not directly related to the hiring process\r\nand employers were not familiar with the entire system. Price agreements were\r\nnot respected.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">But Vendor Management System\r\nis a transparent process, where everybody involved knows about the system. The\r\nmanager can control the hiring process with a single solution. Suppliers are\r\nalso part and parcel of the hiring process.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o>&nbsp;</o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">2.\r\nPrivacy of important documents</span></b><span xss=\"removed\">:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In the traditional hiring\r\nprocess, many documents are needed to apply as a candidate during the hiring\r\nprocess. Later, these documents, even in the printed version, lie here and\r\nthere.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">But, in VMS, important\r\ndocuments are stored centrally along with the assignment. VMS makes use of the\r\ndigital signature software. Thus, a candidate can sign his important documents\r\nwithin VMS. The validity of documents is controlled by VMS.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">3.Guarantee\r\nin price agreements</span></b><span xss=\"removed\">:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">When an organization hires a\r\nlarge number of employees, they cannot manage a wide variety of price\r\nagreements because these agreements are controlled manually. Consequently, employers\r\ncannot get their desired amount, which was decided in agreements. It leads to\r\nfrustrations among employers.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">As VMS is a web-based\r\napplication, price agreements are controlled centrally and applied\r\nautomatically within the system. The risk of error in billing has now reduced\r\nto a minimum level.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">4.\r\nIdentification and management of vendor risk:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In vendor Management System,\r\nwhen performance is measured, the company identifies the problems right away\r\nand can solve the problems before they harm your activities. When the vendor is\r\ncutting corners, whether there is a problem in raw materials or financial\r\nissues etc. are identified with vendor management solutions.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">5.\r\nBoosts vendor performance:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A company gets the quality\r\nstandards it deserves with a <b>vendor management\r\nsolution</b> since it can perform objective assessments of deliverables. The\r\ncompany develops suppliers with specific feedback thus increasing their quality\r\nstandards. This way the company achieves goals it needs.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Role\r\nof United Healthcare Staffing (UHC Staffing) in staffing healthcare staff:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">UHC\r\nHealthcare Staffing</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> provides solutions to healthcare staffing\r\nproblems ranging from billing reports to scheduling staff. UHC Staffing\r\ncontrols staffing issues with Vendor Management System. It provides cost-effective,\r\ntime- saving <b>healthcare staffing\r\nsolutions.</b> Thus it improves quality standards.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span xss=\"removed\">UHC Staffing controls the entire hiring\r\nprocess, which is transparent. Suppliers and employers are integral parts of\r\nthe system.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">UHC Staffing stores important documents\r\ncentrally with vendor management solution.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">It guarantees price agreements, which are\r\ncontrolled centrally with vendor management solution.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">Vendor risk is easily identified by UHC\r\nStaffing. Then, with vendor management solution, it can readily give solutions.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">Last but not the least, UHC Staffing\r\nincreases vendor performance and thus increases quality standards it needs.<o></o></span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Conclusion:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Thus, UHC Staffing plays a\r\nvital and an effective role in controlling healthcare staff. No doubt, they\r\nhandle healthcare staff with care.<o></o></span></p>', 'Vendor Management system ,healthcare staff,UHC Staffing in staffing ,healthcare staffing solutions', 'VENDOR MANAGEMENT SYSTEM: ROLE OF UHC STAFFING IN STAFFING HEALTHCARE STAFF', 'Find Role of United Healthcare Staffing (UHC Staffing) in staffing healthcare staff in USA and Canada', '', 1),
(50, 'SPEECH THERAPIST IN APPLIED BEHAVIOR ANALYSIS (ABA)', 'speech-therapist-in-applied-behavior-analysis-(aba)', '5a12cbaa02323.jpg', '2017-10-26', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Speech\r\nTherapist in Applied Behavior Analysis (ABA)<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Applied\r\nbehavior analysis (ABA)</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> approach includes Speech Language\r\nPathologists (SLP), who provides efficient and effective instruction toward\r\nspeech and language acquisition. This article will tell you about the\r\ndefinition of ABA, what ABA involves and the difference between traditional\r\ninstructional approach and ABA and the role of UHC Staffing in speech therapy\r\napplying ABA principles.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Definition\r\nof Applied Behavior Analysis (ABA):<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">If we break down the term\r\nApplied Behavior Analysis, we get ‘applied\', behavior\' and ‘analysis\'. ‘Applied\'\r\nmeans behavior analysts teach according to behavior analytic principles\r\nsocially significant behaviors like language, play, reading etc. The term\r\n‘behavior\" means responses of children affected by Autism. The responses\r\nare actually teaching targets, which behavior analysts observe and measure. The\r\nterm ‘analysis\'- how the environment affects target behavior.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Here is the example:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Antecedent: say,\r\n\"Toys\".<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Child\'s behavior:\r\n\"Toys\".<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Consequence: \"Here are\r\nyour toys\".<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Behavior\r\nanalysis</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> analyses the events before the response like instruction\r\nand consequences after the response, for example, praise, toys etc. When\r\nbehavior analysts or Speech-Language Pathologists come to know environmental\r\nconditions before and after a child\'s response, they can make a clear idea\r\nabout how to strengthen this response.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">The\r\ngoal of ABA approach:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span xss=\"removed\">The goal of ABA approach has\r\nbeen mentioned below-<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">To equip children with Autism with\r\nspecialized instruction<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">To reduce the individualized support<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">To develop skills that will help children with\r\nAutism to respond accurately to group setting<o></o></span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">It is important to mention\r\nhere that ABA is based on the work of B.F.Skinner, who is a psychologist.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;Now:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The difference between ABA\r\nand Speech Therapy( traditional instructional approach):<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span xss=\"removed\">ABA approach provides intensive,\r\nindividualized instruction.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">ABA approach has positive consequences<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">ABA approach teaches expressive language<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">ABA approach focuses on daily data collection\r\nand analysis of learning variables based on data.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">ABA approach provides errorless learning.<o></o></span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Though <b>speech therapy</b> or traditional instructional approach covers some of\r\nthe areas of ABA approach, speech therapy is quite narrow. It emphasizes on\r\nverbal communication skills like syntax, articulation and the correct use of\r\nlanguage. The basic difference is speech therapy does not address temper\r\ntantrums, motivation, and other behavioral problems.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Speech-language pathologists\r\nare often asked to select an appropriate communication mode for learner because\r\nall learners cannot acquire vocal speech. For those learners, other\r\ncommunication systems are sign language and picture communication. But there\r\nare advantages and disadvantages of each of these systems and neither system\r\nshould be considered fully for the entire classroom. These systems should be\r\napplied according to the needs of each individual.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Requirements\r\nfor SLP jobs (Speech Language Pathologists jobs) and SLPA (Speech Language\r\nPathologists Assistant jobs) jobs:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A\r\nbachelor\'s degree in arts or science or communication science is the minimum requirement\r\nof SLP and SLPA jobs.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Speech Language Pathologists (SLP jobs)</span></b><span xss=\"removed\"> and\r\n<b>Speech-Language Pathologists Assistant\r\n(SLPA jobs) </b>must have a master\'s degree in Audiology and Speech-Language\r\nPathology.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li><span xss=\"removed\">SLP\r\njobs and SLPA jobs require supervised clinical experience of 400 hours.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">Applicants\r\nfor SLPA jobs and SLP jobs must pass the Praxis exam.<o></o></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">The\r\ncandidates applied for the above-mentioned jobs must be licensed.<o></o></span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span xss=\"removed\">Conclusion:<o></o></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Our team of SLPs delivers\r\nefficient and effective instructions to the clients of <b>United Healthcare Staffing (UHC Staffing)</b>. We provide a structured\r\nlearning environment using ABA principles for children with Autism in <b>California</b>. UHC Staffing is offering\r\nSLP jobs and <b>SLPA jobs in California</b>\r\nso that children with Autism and their family receive the maximum benefit from\r\nus.</span></p>', 'Speech Therapist,Speech Therapy ,Speech Therapy Jobs in USA', 'SPEECH THERAPIST IN APPLIED BEHAVIOR ANALYSIS (ABA) USA', 'Find information about SPEECH THERAPIST IN APPLIED BEHAVIOR ANALYSIS (ABA).', '', 1),
(51, 'HOW TO BE A $50M COMPANY IN HEALTHCARE STAFFING', 'how-to-be-a-$50m-company-in-healthcare-staffing', '5a8d39ff2afdd.jpg', '0000-00-00', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">The workforce</span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\"> is the essential requirement of any industry. Be it tourism,\r\neducation or the healthcare industry; good\r\nworkforce can take an organization to the\r\napex. But unfortunately, it’s challenging\r\nto get a good staffing solution for any industry, especially the healthcare industry.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">Here\r\nare some gruesome data that will make you think twice about why a good staffing\r\nsolution is necessary for any healthcare industry.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul xss=\"removed\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">Approx\r\n     25% people believe that patients die due to inefficient healthcare staff<o></o></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">50%\r\n     people blamed understaffing for any injury or harm to patients<o></o></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">85%\r\n     people stated that patients are suffering in hospitals before the number\r\n     of patients assigned to each nurse or other healthcare professional is too\r\n     high</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\">\r\n<br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"></p><p xss=\"removed\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">(</span><span lang=\"EN-IN\"><a href=\"http://advantagemedicalprofessionals.com/blog/importance-of-nurse-staffing-and-patient-safety\"><span xss=\"removed\">Data source</span></a></span></b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\"><b>)</b><br></span>Now\r\nthat you know the importance of staffing solution in the<span xss=\"removed\"> healthcare</span><span xss=\"removed\"> industry and the insufficient number of staffs present\r\nin them, don’t you think that Healthcare Staffing solution providing can be a\r\nlucrative business idea from which you can make a $50M company?</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">But,\r\nthe reality is far away from imagination.\r\nYou can’t make a $50M company overnight. You know Rome too was not built in a\r\nday.<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">So,\r\nwhat to do?<o></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">Here\r\nwe give you can get an idea of\r\nhow to become a $50M company in Healthcare\r\nStaffing.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\"><o></o></span></p><ul xss=\"removed\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">Credentials-\r\n     the</span></b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\"> Proper\r\n     credentialing process can bring huge\r\n     reputation to your company. The\r\n     healthcare industry will trust the staff that you provide<o></o></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">Market\r\n     need-</span></b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\"> Believe me, the healthcare industry is the fastest growing\r\n     industry in the world. So don’t you think that its staffing solution can\r\n     be an excellent business opportunity\r\n     to earn $50M?<o></o></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">Take care\r\n     of your army-</span></b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\"> The existing\r\n     staffs are the backbone of your industry. So keep a proper eye on their mental and physical\r\n     well-being providing a good\r\n     work-life balance.<o></o></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">2-way\r\n     interview</span></b><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">- When you arrange for an\r\n     interview; make sure that not only the interviewer asks a question to the staff for assessing the\r\n     knowledge, but the staff should also\r\n     know about the environment where he/she is going to work. This will help in high retention rate and\r\n     make your organization a successful staffing solution.<o></o></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xss=\"removed\">If\r\nyou think you are a determined soul and make your healthcare staffing business\r\na $50M company, then no one can stop you.\r\nJust stick to your goal. Work harder, think deeper, stay fit and soon you rock\r\nthe stage of healthcare staffing industry.<o></o></span></p><p xss=\"removed\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Healthcare staffing company in california,Medical Staffing Company in California ', 'HOW TO BE A $50M COMPANY IN HEALTHCARE STAFFING', 'Here we give you can get an idea of how to become a $50M company in Healthcare Staffing.', 'HEALTHCARE STAFFING', 1),
(52, 'HOME HEALTH PHYSICAL THERAPY JOBS ON DEMAND', 'home-health-physical-therapy-jobs-on-demand', '5aa2604ec4bd2.jpg', '0000-00-00', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Physical therapy is a\r\nlot in demand in the present day environment.Physical therapy helps\r\nindividualsto improve their daily strength and do rigorous work with more\r\nflexibility. More and more patients are flocking to allied health professions\r\nlike physical therapists for exercise therapy, manual therapy and\r\nelectrotherapy. Thus, physical therapy jobs are facing increasing demand but it\r\nis important that you choose the right physical therapist who can cater to your\r\nmobility needs. We all want someone we can trust when it comes to matters of\r\nhealth, don’t we?<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In my opinion, physical\r\ntherapists at UHC are very well trained and in possession of all the modern\r\nmachines and technologies that are required to make you fit and healthy again. <o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Hospitals generally\r\nprovide such services to all those who have been subject to disabling diseases,\r\ntraumatic injuries or even congenital services. <o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o>&nbsp;</o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Home health physical\r\ntrainers are basically those people who have a certified degree in physical\r\ntraining and are available and employed in various health centers. The job\r\nprofiles of such personnel basically include their need to go and visit the\r\nhomes of the patient if they have been physically injured or are bed-ridden. If\r\nyou are already a holder of a degree in physical training, this is your call,\r\nas physical trainers are well in demand. Most importantly, the physical\r\ntrainers willing to visit and serve the patients at home are an added bonus to\r\nthis industry and all experienced individuals are welcome at <b>UHC Staffing</b>.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o>&nbsp;</o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Services offered by\r\nPhysical Therapists:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Gait\r\ntraining<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Gross\r\nmotor development<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Strength\r\nand flexibility training<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Orthotic\r\nand prosthetic training<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Tone\r\nmanagement<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Sports\r\nphysical therapy.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o>&nbsp;</o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The job seekers are\r\nexpected to be able to handle the following:<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Handling\r\nvarious techniques and the tasks involved depending on the nature of the\r\nproblem and the age of the patient.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Identifying\r\nthe problem of the patient and planning a relevant program to help him recover.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Scheduling\r\nand proper implementation of the plan of work<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Working\r\nwith a personal attachment and involvement for every client and making them\r\nfully satisfied.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Maintenance\r\nof a proper job record in handling clients.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Monitoring\r\nand finally evaluating the client\'s initial to final progress.<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><o>&nbsp;</o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span xss=\"removed\">So, if you’re a physical therapist who would\r\nlike to contribute for the betterment of patients they serve or you’re looking\r\nfor an experienced one you can trust with your health issues, you can always go\r\nto UHC Staffing.&nbsp;</span>', 'Home health physical therapy ,physical therapy jobs,Physical therapy nursing jobs', 'HOME HEALTH PHYSICAL THERAPY JOBS ON DEMAND', 'Find the best HOME HEALTH PHYSICAL THERAPY JOBS in USA and Canada.', 'HOME HEALTH PHYSICAL THERAPY JOBS', 1);
